description: The Gargano family is taking their 55 years of restaurant experience and talent for crafting delicious Italian cuisine through the streets of Baltimore, and everybody is feeling the amoré for the really tasty array of pasta, subs, salads, and other Italian classics being served on these wheels. The Italians subs are scrumptious and huge, stuffed with options like Sausage, Green Peppers, & Onion, Porchetta (slow-roasted seasoned pork heaped on a sub roll and topped with broccoli rabe), Caprese, and Chicken Parmigiana--and these are only just a few!Folks are raving about the pasta too, like the creamy Mushroom Ravioli, Fusilli Bolognese, and the Penne Pasta topped with broccoli rabe, sausage, and goat cheese. For a mobile menu with all this and more, you just must make your way straight to Pasta La Vista, Baby!
name: Pasta La Vista Baby
